	(1283,'5','6',1,1,2,0,0,'AH-06-1.1.2','Students will identify instruments according to classifications.  Family - brass, woodwind, string, percussion; Voices - soprano, alto, tenor, bass; Folk - instruments used in folk music; Orchestral - instruments used in contemporary orchestral settings.\r\n',5),
