	(1324,'5','7',2,1,1,3,1,'AH-07-2.1.1','Students will analyze or explain how diverse cultures and time periods are reflected in music.  Periods:\r\nClassical Greece â Presents the universal ideal of beauty through logic, order, reason and moderation. (Pythagorean â music theory based on mathematical logic); Medieval â Appeals to the emotions and stresses the importance of religion. (Gregorian chant).\r\n',5),
